DirectConnect
From iA wiki
See Also: Decentralized Clients
Home page (Windows): http://www.neo-modus.com
Home page (multiplatform): http://dcgui.berlios.de
Home page (DC++): http://dcplusplus.sourceforge.net (Sourceforge)
DirectConnect is a file sharing application for Windows. The network is semi-centralized: Some users run so-called hubs, which are centralized servers that manage user indexing, file indexing, and chat. Once a user is connected to a hub, he will immediately find himself in the hub's chat channel and see a list of the users connected to that hub. He can then browse individual users' files and download interesting
